      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just a chemical reaction with heat. it almost feels like there's some kind of \"magic\" happening in the oven to change the texture and color like that all at once. is there anything else that can mess with it or change how intense the color gets?",
      "source": "evaluator"
